[Exploratory analysis on burden of disease attributable to asbestosis from 2006 
to 2015].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Liu MX(1), Zhu XJ, Li T, Xiao P, Wang D.

Author information:
(1)National Institute of Occupational Health and Poison Control, Chinese Center 
