Ovarian conservation vs removal at the time of benign hysterectomy.

Adelman MR(1), Sharp HT(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, University of Utah, Salt Lake City, 
UT. Electronic address: marisa.adelman@hsc.utah.edu.
(2)Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, University of Utah, Salt Lake City, 
