Use of Proteomics To Investigate Kidney Function Decline over 5 Years.

Carlsson AC(1)(2), Ingelsson E(2)(3)(4), Sundström J(2)(5), Jesus Carrero J(6), 
Gustafsson S(2), Feldreich T(2)(7), Stenemo M(2), Larsson A(2), Lind L(2), 
